reviewText: Would like to get the rest of the series.... but has proved difficult to find.

Probably the funniest and non annoying kid cartoon available. I was quite surprised to find this to be educational, although in a very unconventional way. I really don't know too much about the graphics because while my son is watching I am doing other things, but I find myself chuckling quite a bit just listening to the dialogue.
We love this show. Super funny. It arrived quickly and was as we  expected. We will definitely be buying the next disc soon.

World of quest: The Quest Begins This DVD has 10 exciting adventures of Prince Nestor who tries to save his parents with the help of Quest, who would really prefer to just be left alone instead of being coerced to use his special powers to help the prince. The adventures are fun for  elementary kids, especially boys.
